<div class="rounded-xl px-6 pb-12 pt-16 lg:px-8 mt-18">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
    <h2
      class="font-sans text-4xl font-bold leading-relaxed tracking-tight text-black sm:text-5xl"
    >
      Compare Helperbird Plans
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-6 font-sans text-xl leading-relaxed text-black">
      Take a look at the different Helperbird plans and see which one works best
      for you. If you need any help, our friendly support team is always here to
      assist!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div
